# 📖 Introduction

I'm Jules—an emerging creative professional passionate about design, storytelling, and visual communication.

I specialize in transforming complex technical ideas into clean, accessible, and engaging visuals. My creative journey began with hand-drawn school posters and has evolved into professional-level design work supported by a strong foundation in digital media, design strategy, and communication theory.

Throughout my academic and professional experiences, I have led design initiatives for conferences, marketing campaigns, student organizations, and technical events. Whether developing a complete brand identity or designing a time-sensitive promotional campaign, I approach every project with research, intention, and attention to detail.

I believe great design goes beyond aesthetics—it's about communicating ideas clearly, creating memorable experiences, and inspiring action.

